<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Her Real Housewives of Atlanta co-star Cynthia Bailey proudly declared she's gained the Covid 20 and noted her fiance Mike Hill 'ain't complaining' after cruel trolls comment on her weight.</p>

<p>And one day later, Kandi Burruss took to her Instagram stories to reveal that she is starting her new workout regimen with a goal of losing 30 pounds.</p>

<p>The reality star, 44, explained that she gained 20 pounds since May, and even then was trying to lose 10 pounds, leaving her at 30 pounds as her weight loss goal.</p>

<p>The latest: Kandi Burruss took to her Instagram stories to reveal that she is starting her new workout regimen with a goal of losing 30 pounds on Wednesday morning</p>

<p>The TV star kicked off her stories with: 'Ok so today is Wednesday, I believe its the, is it the 16th of September? This is the first day back to working out.'</p>

<p>Kandi continued: 'I gained 20 pounds since May. Since you know... well not at the beginning of Covid.'</p>

<p>Adding: 'The beginning of Covid i was working out and i was in shape. And even then I wanted to lose 10 pounds but I ended up getting lax and comfortable and I ended up gaining 20.'</p>

<p>'So that means I have have 30 pounds of which I would like to lose. I just want to better myself overall. I just want to get used to making working out a regular routine.'</p>

<p>Candid: The reality star, 44, explained that she gained 20 pounds since May, and even then was trying to lose 10 pounds, leaving her at 30 pounds as her weight loss goal</p>

<p>Workout plans: The TV star kicked off her stories with: 'Ok so today is Wednesday, I believe its the, is it the 16th of September? This is the first day back to working out'</p>

<p>Her plans: Kandi continued: 'I gained 20 pounds since May. Since you know... well not at the beginning of Covid'</p>

<p>Kandi revealed that her cousin Patrick has volunteered to work out with her: 'He's a trainer. He got up and came to my house at 7 to workout and that's going to be my regular time.'</p>

<p>She concluded her stories with: 'I hope I can stick to this.' </p>

<p>Kandi captioned the video with: 'I need help! Thank God for family... I hope I can stick to this 7 am workout schedule.'</p>

<p>The brunette beauty was most recently seen on September 11 with husband Todd Tucker and their son Ace Wells, four; they are also parents to daughter Blaze Tucker, 10 months. Blaze was born via surrogate. </p>

<p>Kandi also has a daughter named Riley, 18, and is stepmom to Todd's daughter Kaela, 23. </p>

